text: Antria Michail (born 19 December 1991) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a midfielder for First Division club Lefkothea Latsion and the Cyprus women's national team. ==Career== Michail has been capped for the Cyprus national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Apollon Ladies F.C. players
